Package se.miun.itm.input.util

Class Summary
EnvironmentInfo A util that collects environmental information via Java.
InputStreamWrapper A helpers class that clones input streams in order to make them readable multiple times.
ParamInitializer The ParamInitializer organizes the input parameters according to the logical dependency order in which they have to be instantiated.
ParamUtil A class upplying basic features to support the extraction of information from param elements or parsing and processing of id related services.
Q A help class that contains all the identifiers of objects and concepts used in InPUT.
TreeSorter Orders the parameter tree with respect to the numerical parameter min-max dependencies.
